Release Info

MotoGPT15 is back with a range of new features to guarantee an even
more comprehensive and compelling experience. The career mode has been
expanded with the introduction of Personal Teams, the AI and physics have
been overhauled and optimized with improved interaction between bike and
rider, and a new game mode sees you trying to beat the times set by the
best riders in each category.
